sentence.text: In this study, we examine the role of proton-sensing ovarian cancer G protein-coupled receptor 1 (inflammatory response) in extracellular acidification-induced regulation of cyclooxygenase (generation of precursor metabolites and energy)-2 induction, PGI(2) production, MAPK phosphatase (MKP)-1 expression, and plasminogen activator inhibitor (regulation of signaling receptor activity)-1 expression and proliferation in human aortic smooth muscle cells (AoSMCs).
